data.enText: a private room on a large ship

data.chText: （政府要员或王室成员等使用的）会客厅，议事厅，国事活动厅
data.enText: a room used by important government members, members of a royal family, etc. on formal occasions

word_means: 会客厅，议事厅，国事活动厅

means: (政府要员或王室成员等使用的)会客厅，议事厅，国事活动厅

value.def: On a passenger ship, a stateroom is a private room, especially one that is large and comfortable.
In a palace or other impressive building, a stateroom is a large room for use on formal occasions.
